  <brief_title>Matrix Metalloproteinases Neutralizing Agents in Oral Lichen Planus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Matrix Metalloproteinase Neutralizing Agent in Treatment of Oral Lichen Planus: A Pilot Study</official_title>
