  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The current study will be conducted to evaluate the effectiveness of matrix
      metalloproteinases inhibitors on erosive oral lichen planus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Matrix metalloproteinases inhibitor (Orochem) will be given to patients with Oral erosive
      lichen planus three times daily for 3 weeks. Then the subjective discomfort and pain severity
      as well as the objective disease severity scores will be collected.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
